There isn't a way to specifically target NES.  You just have to get it to make a raw binary (if it doesn't by default, there should be a command-line option).<br /><br />Then you'll need to either put the iNES header in your source, or copy it onto the rom afterwards.<br /><br />It's been a long time since I used DASM, I can't remember how everything worked though.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=10">Memblers</a> — Sat Nov 20, 2004 7:42 pm</p><hr />
